videos.description: A 2-yard score by Devin Singletary caps a 10-play, 75-yard opening drive to put Florida Atlantic up early.
videos.headline: Singletary finishes 10-play drive with TD run

videos.description: Owls' RB Devin Singletary powers the ball past the goal line from 3 yards out to go up 14-0.
videos.headline: Singletary scores second TD on another powerful run

videos.description: Owls' QB Jason Driskel fools the Mean Green defense with a play-action fake and finds Willie Wright behind the secondary for a 69-yard score.
videos.headline: Driskel connects with Wright for 69-yard score

videos.description: North Texas QB Mason Fine throws a dart to O'Keeron Rutherford over the middle for the Mean Green's first score of the day.
videos.headline: 'Fine' pass puts North Texas on the board

videos.description: The Owls' offense sprints to the ball and Jason Driskel scores on a quarterback sneak before the North Texas defense is in position.
videos.headline: Owls fly to the line and score on sneak

videos.description: Owls' RB Devin Singletary's third score of the day comes on a shifty 22-yard run to the pylon as the Owls go up 38-7 before half.
videos.headline: Singletary sets school record with 14th rushing TD of season

videos.description: Harrison Bryant makes the catch and is hit by a Mean Green defender, but extends to cross the pylon to go up 48-10.
videos.headline: Second effort gives Owls another red zone TD
